# projects.conf — registry of projects that use ai-containers
#
# Each line is an absolute path to a project root whose .ai-containers/
# subdirectory should be kept in sync with this repo.
#
# Managed by project-init.sh — you can also add/remove lines manually.
# This file is gitignored; projects.conf.example is the committed template.
#
# Example:
# /home/user/dev/myproject
# /home/user/dev/another-project
